-march-5-2019|title=Top 10 Country Albums: March 5, 2019|first=Matt|last=Bjorke|date=  February 20, 2019|work=Roughstock|accessdate=April 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref |region=United States |artist=Thomas Rhett |title=Life Changes |type=album }}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Center Point Road]]''\n|\n* Release date: May 31, 2019\n* Label: Valory\n| 1\n| 1\n| 24\n| 2\n| \u2014\n|\n* US: 101,600<ref>{{cite news|url=http://roughstock.com/news/2020/03/44152-top-10-country-albums-in-pure-sales-march-2-2020|title=Top 10 Country Albums In Pure Sales: March 2, 2020|work=Roughstock|first=Matt |last=Bjorke |date=March 3, 2020|accessdate= March 7, 2020}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| colspan=\"10\" style=\"font-size:8pt\"| \"\u2014\" denotes releases that did not chart.\n|}\n\n== Extended plays ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\"| Title\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Details\n! colspan=\"3\"| Peak chart positions\n|- style=\"font-size:smaller;\"\n! style=\"width:4em;\"| [[Top Country Albums|US Country]]<br><ref name=\"Country Albums\" />\n! style=\"width:4em;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br><ref name=\"Billboard 200\" />\n! style=\"width:4em;\"| [[Top Heatseekers|US<br>Heat]]<br><ref name=\"billboard1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/419550/thomas-rhett/chart?f=324 |title=Thomas Rhett - Chart history |publisher=Billboard |date= |accessdate=2013-08-28}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Thomas Rhett (EP)|Thomas Rhett]]''\n| \n* Release date: August 28, 2012\n* Label: Valory\n| 24\n| 133\n| 3\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n===As lead artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Single\n! colspan=\"6\"| Peak chart positions\n! rowspan=\"2\"| Sales\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:12em;\"| [[Music recording sales certifications|Certifications]]<br>{{small|([[List of best selling music 